    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Actor that provides services in the context of Technology</skos:definition>
    <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">"Partner" is a vague term and should not be used - instead the more specific terms provided in this vocabulary should be used. Partner refers to entities that provide services for the technology (as opposed to for using the technology) - for example to further develop or refine it, or to test or audit it.</skos:scopeNote>
